name: H1
description:
hi part 2 - audio version

Every sound you hear is a variation of the word hi.

There are silent parts in the beat, that display the "hhh" sound of the word hi. Almost sounds like someone breathing.
Spooky vibes for #HENhalloween. A day late but I made this yesterday during halloween.

Only other samples used are for the drum beat. 
The drum beat has an automated Saturator behind it to give it that fat, future effect.

I work on Ableton Live.
